<p><strong>Note:</strong> <span style="text-decoration: underline;">2/15/18</span><br />
<em><tt><strong>THIS IS AN AUTOMATED MESSAGE</strong> DR GREGORY HAS BEEN TRAPPED INSIDE A HARD DRIVE IN HIS OFFICE AT SITE-17. REQUESTING IMMEDIATE ASSISTANCE AND SERVING OF MEDICATION.<br />
