~Rosen</p>
</blockquote>
<p><strong>Note:</strong> <span style="text-decoration: underline;">3/28/2019</span><br />
<em>Dear Rosen. The robotic limb you provided me is constantly flipping people off. I will readily admit it was a bit funny, but it just flipped off the site director. Can you send someone down to have a look at it? I believe it to be self-aware, but I want a second opinion before I classify it as an SCP.</em><br />
<em>- Assistant Researcher N.C.E.</em></p>
