<p>Looks like somebody installed the A.N.G.E.R drives by mistake, stands for Automatic Non-discriminating Gross Energetic Rudeness. It's a custom job, made to fit folks with robotic limbs who feel phantom limb syndrome continuing after they get the replacement. Basically makes it act somewhat autonomously in a method which matches the 'personality' of the phantom limb so as to help it disappear. Kinda neat, huh? Anyways, just bring it on down to the workshop at your leisure and I can fix it up for ya.<br />
~Rosen</p>
</blockquote>
<p><strong>Note:</strong> <span style="text-decoration: underline;">3/29/2019</span><br />
<em>David. Assistant Researcher N.C.E. was found dead on the floor of his office. He appears to have been strangled, and his prosthetic is missing. I'm don't exactly understand electronics, but is there some way you can track the arm remotely?</em><br />
<em>- Security Chief Ozark</em></p>
