~Rosen</p>
</blockquote>
<p><strong>Note:</strong> <span style="text-decoration: underline;">6/7/19</span><br />
<em>So&#8230; Rosen. I attempted to do some work, and my computer was replaced with a computer-shaped lump of Play-Doh. I know it’s not an anomaly since the site I’m working at stores no anomalous items, and is more just a data center.</em><br />
